commit_message:
Update SRA_to_bam.txt

Requires a text file called 'toDownload' listing the paths to the SRA files. The base directory is 'ftp://ftp-trace.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sra/sra-instant/reads/ByExp/sra/'.
Update and rename Processing ChIP-seq from SRA files to SRA_to_bam.txt

Update BAM to GRanges.R

The Rsamtools function readGappedAlignments() has been superseded by the GenomicRanges function readGAlignments().

Update SAMtoBAM.sh

Edited loop to change location of samfiles to current directory.

Update SAMtoBAM.sh

Compile a list of SAM files within a directory, remove the .sam extension and convert to BAM files.

Create samfiles.sh

Compile a list of samfiles and remove the extension.
Update and rename SAMtoBAM to SAMtoBAM.sh

Create BAM to GRanges.R

Read a BAM file into R and then convert to GRanges object.

Create RemoveSRDuplicates.R

Output is ReadAligned object for use in R.

Create fastqFilterLoop.sh

'FilesToFilter' is list of Fastq files that will be filtered.

Create illuminaQualFilter.R

"file_to_filter.txt" lists a single FastQ file. To batch this loop your filenames into "file_to_filter.txt"

Update Processing ChIP-seq from SRA files

Added BOWTIE2_INDEXES designation. Bowtie now working.
Create qualFilter.R QC for FastQ files

Create getfiles.sh

This script downloads SRA files from NCBI. It requires an object called 'allfiles' containing the latter part of the path to each .sra file you wish to download.

Download and install prebuilt Bowtie indexes

This script downloads and unzips Bowtie indexes.

Create Processing ChIP-seq from SRA files

This script downloads SRA files from NCBI, converts them to FastQ, aligns them to the relevant genome using Bowtie2 and runs MACs to call peaks.
